<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<p><strong>Summary:</strong></p>
<p>Depending on whether the&nbsp;<strong>10x CAP API</strong> needs to be s=
plit, we can determine if an <strong>additional EXP API</strong> is require=
d.</p>
<p><br><strong>Action:</strong><br>
 Account Team to evaluate the need for API split and advise on EXP API requ=
irements.</p>
<p><br></p>
<p><strong>Target to Complete:</strong><br>
 Sprint 4 ends 20 Aug 2025</p>
<p><br></p>
<p><time datetime=3D"2025-09-22" class=3D"date-past">22 Sep 2025</time> Reo=
pen the dependency as there is a pending decision from the WASH team to spl=
it the Arrangement API and the Overdraft facility API, this change would po=
tentially be impacting the Channel EXP API and the One Core Arrangement API=
.&nbsp;</p>
<p><br></p>
<p><strong>Action: </strong></p>
<p>Decision updates/swagger from the WASH / Account team</p>
<p><br></p>
<p><time datetime=3D"2025-10-14" class=3D"date-past">14 Oct 2025</time>&nbs=
p; A new WASH endpoint and W1C endpoint to be built to retrieve Overdraft l=
imit/rate and override from 10x. New EXP API to be built to retrieve overdr=
aft limits and debit rates for display purpose.&nbsp;</p>
</div></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<p>&nbsp;<time datetime=3D"2025-08-11" class=3D"date-past">11 Aug 2025</tim=
e>&nbsp;</p>
</div></td>
