<h2 id=3D"id-09.SD:Overdraft(Arranged&amp;IDOL)LimitsandPricing-KeyDecision=
s"><span>Key Decisions</span></h2>
<p></p>
<p><br></p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table class=3D"wrapped confluenceTable">
<colgroup class=3D"">
<col class=3D"">
<col class=3D"">
<col class=3D"">
<col class=3D"">
<col class=3D"">
</colgroup>
<tbody class=3D"">
<tr class=3D"">
<th style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTh">=
<strong>Ref #</strong></th>
<th style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTh">=
<strong><span data-teams=3D"true">Decision&nbsp;</span></strong></th>
<th style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTh">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper"><strong>Description</strong>
</div></th>
<th style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTh">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper"><strong>Decision made by</strong>
</div></th>
<th style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTh">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper"><strong>Status&nbsp;</strong>
</div></th>
</tr>
<tr class=3D"">
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
#001</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
<p>Available balance to include Overdraft limit&nbsp;</p><p><br></p><p><br>=
</p><p><br></p></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<p><strong>Decision Log:</strong></p>
<p>&nbsp;6 Aug 2025: Align balance descriptions with Trading Bank (no limit=
s included). Decision to remove overdraft limit column due to low usage (on=
ly ~5% of the book).</p>
<p>13 Aug 2025: Confirm TB accounts have arranged limits in available balan=
ce but no IDOL limit. Navleen has different requirements for 10x vs. mirror=
ed accounts. &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>
<p>15 Aug 2025: Confirmed with the below:</p>
<ul>
<li>Available balance for mirrored accounts =3D current balance + EOD limit=
</li>
<li>Available balance for 10x accounts =3D current balance + EOD limit + ID=
OL limit</li>
</ul>
<p><br></p>
<p><strong>Owner:</strong></p>
<p>Hong Ly&nbsp; &nbsp;</p>
</div></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
Hong Ly&nbsp; &nbsp;</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
Deferred. TB mirrored account won't be in scope for Feb.&nbsp;<br><br>
 The definition for 10x account will follow the requirement.&nbsp;</td>
</tr>
<tr class=3D"">
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
#002</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
W1C Facility endpoint availability on Feb release</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
<p>The <strong>W1C Arrangement API</strong> currently handles multiple fina=
ncial facilities, including overdraft. However, due to its increasing compl=
exity, <strong>Andrew Suduk</strong> has proposed <strong>splitting out the=
 overdraft facility into a separate endpoint</strong>.</p><p>This suggestio=
n was raised after Andrew highlighted the architectural complexity of the W=
1C API to Stuart</p><p>&nbsp;<strong>Decision</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>The <strong>dedicated overdraft endpoint</strong> will <strong>not be d=
elivered in February</strong> due to delivery timeline constraints.</li>
<li>Instead, <strong>Andrew proposes a May delivery</strong> for the new ov=
erdraft-specific API.</li>
<li>As an <strong>interim solution</strong>, <strong>Stuart agreed</strong>=
 that the <strong>EXP API can directly call the WASH API</strong>, bypassin=
g the W1C facility API.</li>
</ul></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<p><strong><a class=3D"confluence-userlink user-mention" data-username=3D"M=
037818" href=3D"/display/~M037818" data-linked-resource-id=3D"7244962" data=
-linked-resource-version=3D"1" data-linked-resource-type=3D"userinfo" data-=
base-url=3D"https://confluence.srv.westpac.com.au">Stuart Murdoch</a> </str=
ong></p>
<p><strong><a class=3D"confluence-userlink user-mention" data-username=3D"M=
062050" href=3D"/display/~M062050" data-linked-resource-id=3D"1515690289" d=
ata-linked-resource-version=3D"1" data-linked-resource-type=3D"userinfo" da=
ta-base-url=3D"https://confluence.srv.westpac.com.au">Andrew Suduk</a></str=
ong></p>
<p><strong><a class=3D"confluence-userlink user-mention" data-username=3D"M=
064489" href=3D"/display/~M064489" data-linked-resource-id=3D"1920714325" d=
ata-linked-resource-version=3D"1" data-linked-resource-type=3D"userinfo" da=
ta-base-url=3D"https://confluence.srv.westpac.com.au">Edmond Tso</a> <br><a=
 class=3D"confluence-userlink user-mention" data-username=3D"M065552" href=
=3D"/display/~M065552" data-linked-resource-id=3D"2096187630" data-linked-r=
esource-version=3D"1" data-linked-resource-type=3D"userinfo" data-base-url=
=3D"https://confluence.srv.westpac.com.au">Rajeev Ranjan</a> </strong></p>
<p><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>
</div></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
Completed</td>
</tr>
<tr class=3D"">
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
#003</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
<br></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
